install terraform

go to google chrome and type terraform install we can get hashcorp terraform site download windows amdb and install terraform.exe file

and set the environment variables for terraform

terraform --version

Terraform v1.8.2 on windows_amd64

install aws cli

download the msi version of windows in google

create one iam user in aws

iam-->users-->create user-->next-->attach permissions-->admin access-->next-->create user

once user is created go to security creds and create access keys

open cmd and do the below to configure aws

aws configure